        <b>What is Surface Area?</b> The surface area of an object is defined as the total area of the <i>surface</i> of the
        3-dimensional object. The surface is the outermost region of an object.
      </p>
      <p>
        In this unit, we will calculate surface area of various shapes with <i>smooth surfaces</i>.
